          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Np-237 fission chamber - for neutron beam",
                "monitoring."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  4pi detector for delayed neutrons registration-"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " consisted of thirty  B-10 proportional counters",
                "SNM-11 in polyethylene. Protected by boron carbide,",
                "borated polyethylene, cadmium .",
                " Neutron registration dead time 2.3+- 0.2 microsec.",
                " Standard Am(Li) and Pu(Li) sources were used to",
                " monitor stability of detector .",
                " Energy dependence of neutron detector was calculated",
                "by Monte-Carlo method and absolute normalization by",
                "data of detector efficiency measured via V-51(p,n)Cr-51",
                "reaction and Cf-252 spontaneous fission source."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The irradiation time intervals were 15,180 and",
                "300 s. Depending on background conditions the delayed",
                "neutron counting intervals were 424.5 and 724.5 s with",
                "the time channel sequence after the end of sample",
                "irradiation: 0.01s (150 channels), 0.02s (150 channels)",
                ", 0.1 s (200 channels), 1 s (200 channels) and 10 s (30",
                " or 50 channels).",
                "The times of sample transportation from the irradiation",
                "position to the neutron detector were from 150 to 200ms",
                "depending on gas pressure and the weight of samples."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " No information."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For backgrounds:",
                "Counting interval, s             724.5      224.5",
                "Relative background, %           1.10-1.84  0.35-0.58",
                "Intensity of background,n/s               0.16"
              ]
            }
          ],
